1. 3 weeks before DAoC comes out, they block server numbers. They even said it was because they didn't want competition getting thier numbers. Ummm, well, lesse here....they haven't had em blocked all year, so there has been ample time to compile all the info anyone needed. They did this because they don't want others &quot;following the crowd&quot;....saying &quot;Gee, half the server is gone, I wonder if DAoC is that good ?&quot; Gamers are a social breed, if people leave, it generally is in droves.<br>
